/* Gogo Language Texts

Table of Contents

02.User Login, Logout, Register
03.Menu
04.Error Page
*/


module.exports = {
  /* 01.General */

  /* 02.User Login, Logout, Register */
  "user.login-title": "Login",
  "user.register": "Register",

  "menu.reports": "Reports",

  "menu.survey": "Survey",
  "menu.todo": "Todo",
  "menu.search" :"Search",
  "menu.docs": "Docs",
  "menu.blank-page": "Blank Page",

 /* 04.Error Page */
 "pages.error-title": "Ooops... looks like an error occurred!",
 "pages.error-code": "Error code",
 "pages.go-back-home": "GO BACK HOME",

  /* Error Messages */

  "INVALID_USER": "There is no such user or password is not correct",
  "INVALID_CREDENTIALS": "There is no such user or password is not correct",
